### ============================================
### PRUEBAS - OBTENER DATOS
### ============================================

### Obtener todas las categorías
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/item-categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener todos los items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtener items de la categoría "Granos" (ID 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/category/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Buscar items con "Arroz"
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/search?name=Arroz
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

